%% Status: NEEDS HUMAN REVIEW
%% A-branch solution: End-to-end exploration flow
%% Ties together GPS → cell visit → stats update → infographic refresh → encounter
sequenceDiagram
    participant Player
    participant MapTab
    participant GPS
    participant CellService
    participant StatsService
    participant Supabase
    participant InfographicScreen

    Player->>MapTab: open Map tab
    MapTab->>MapTab: show WorldScreen (default)

    Player->>MapTab: drill down to PlayerScreen
    MapTab->>GPS: request position
    GPS-->>MapTab: lat, lng

    MapTab->>CellService: position update (lat, lng)
    CellService->>CellService: determine current Voronoi cell
    CellService->>CellService: resolve cell → district → city → state → country

    alt New cell visit
        CellService->>Supabase: INSERT v3_cell_visits (user_id, cell_id)
        Supabase-->>CellService: confirmed

        CellService->>StatsService: recompute hierarchy stats
        StatsService->>StatsService: district: cells_visited / cells_total
        StatsService->>StatsService: city: districts_touched / districts_total
        StatsService->>StatsService: state: cities_touched / cities_total
        StatsService->>StatsService: country: states_touched / states_total

        Note over StatsService: Stats cached client-side,<br/>recomputed on cell visit

        CellService-->>MapTab: cell visit recorded + fog cleared
    end

    Player->>MapTab: pinch-close from PlayerScreen
    MapTab->>InfographicScreen: show DistrictScreen
    InfographicScreen->>InfographicScreen: refresh cell grid with new visit highlighted

    Player->>MapTab: pinch-close from DistrictScreen
    MapTab->>InfographicScreen: show CityScreen
    InfographicScreen->>InfographicScreen: refresh district cards with updated %

    Note over CellService,Supabase: Encounter trigger connects to<br/>existing 6-1 discovery-to-pack flow
